Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:04.38,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mō tomerarenai my sweet song
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:09.09,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}nakisō na koe de I love you
